    {
      "type": "text", "id": "cat1_body",
      "x": 140, "y": 355, "width": 280, "height": 280,
      "text": "🖼️  canvas-design\n      posters + static art\n\n🎛️  algorithmic-art\n      p5.js generative art\n\n🎞️  slack-gif-creator\n      animated GIFs\n\n🎨  theme-factory\n      style any artifact\n\n💻  frontend-design\n      polished React/HTML\n\n🏷️  brand-guidelines\n      Anthropic brand style",
      "originalText": "🖼️  canvas-design\n      posters + static art\n\n🎛️  algorithmic-art\n      p5.js generative art\n\n🎞️  slack-gif-creator\n      animated GIFs\n\n🎨  theme-factory\n      style any artifact\n\n💻  frontend-design\n      polished React/HTML\n\n🏷️  brand-guidelines\n      Anthropic brand style",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
